the sindelfingen plant about 15 miles west of stuttgart is only 
the second plant in the world that will mass produce the complex 
semiconductors for ibm officials said monday 
productionline manufacturing began in burlington vt a few 
months ago and another ibm manufacturing plant is scheduled to 
open in yasu japan later this year according to peter w thonis 
